text:
To mere baccho k Singapore waale Uncle,
Sahi ka God aadmi hai tu. Poore campus ka sbse confident launda hai kuch bhi pull off krskta hai. Bhai  koi side hobby chahiye to btana mera therapist bnjaana shauk shauk me hi, paise ki to zrurt hai nhi aise hi crorepati aadmi hai tu. Tere se kabhi ego clash hua hi nhi kyuki alag league me khelta hai tu. Baaki ye Pratham launde ki deal kya hai? Abhi tak nhi samajh aaya mjhe XD. Baaki gupta ki to maarskta tha prank call me Abdul Gaffur se gndi fati thi meri.

text: Aur bhai koi shampoo, detergent, saabun k ad me zrurt ho to please yaad krna apna bhi chotta sa sapna hai :P

text:
Aur Digumarthu Komal Emmanuel Raju bhaii!!
Mai to abhi bhi bolta hu jis din tu apne me aaya sabki phaad dega. Mast sweet aadmi tha tu. Though we kinda drifted apart from third year but the finale night definitely was a closure to all of it. AIse hi humble, down to earth, sweet aur chaapu rehna bhai . The world needs more people like you. All the best bhaii for your future.
Bajpai!!
author: Somesh  Bajpai

text:
Avisha, I will always be jealous of your happy-go-lucky attitude. The first day I met you, you said to me that I do not look the same as in my DP, and I haven't forgiven you for that. I've also taught you Phy 102, if you remember. EE labs were a nightmare for me, but somehow you and Priya were able to pull it off. Also, you always got the easier ones in viva.
All the best for your future now that you're venturing into something new and exciting.
author: Somesh  Bajpai

text:
To Ayush Sharma,
On behalf of SBG villa, we congratulate you on your IIMA selection. Therefore, we would like to extend our first invitation to our elite club, where you'll get exclusive access to SBG parties.

Sincerely,
SBG Management

Chalo done with the formalities. Kitni epic nights hui hai bhai saath me. Kaafi phases dekhe hai apun ne to ek dusre k. Poora mean girls episodes bhi chale hai apne . Bc Ecell mjhe bhi join krlena the regret hota hai. Keep hustling kam fraud maar. 
Bajpai!!
author: Somesh  Bajpai

text: I could write tons of things about you being funny, your useless skills here but I don't think there is any point in talking about the past because the future is set to be like gold. See you in Bangalore soon sweetheart I can feel some grand things are waiting for us. They're going to bow down to our supremacy :P

text: We've had our differences bohot. You have been super rude to me at times. Thankfully I had Naman to bitch about you. At the same time, I also did feel comfortable being vulnerable with you. I remember that moment in Varanasi jab in the end we were looking at the pooja from ghat and I told you take a snapshot of that. I am pretty sure your next phase in US will change you from Rude Karen to less rude karen. Please New York ghuma dena.
author: Somesh  Bajpai

text:
Tmhe aur tmhaare roomie ko hmaari wing ne adopt krliya warna udhar tmhara character development to kya hi hota. Dus saal baad mjhe terrace k woh philosophical dicussions zrur yaad aayenge. Movie nights to kya mast plan out horhi thi. Aur Sanjana kitni fake thi bc. Shaam ko canteen me chai samose khaake mast emo boiis dekhna kya sahi zindagi thi. Also "Don't do that". Better location overcast weather pe wo scene reshoot krskte hai professionally. Script me potential to bohot hai.
Your D139 Roomie
Bajpai!!

text: It was very tough for me to keep up with your crazy,  carefree attitude. And I haven't taken any sides, though it really doesn't matter now. And yes, those unexpected calls at certain points can be everything you need. Keep those memes coming. Bangalore plans did get canceled, but I would definitely love to meet you in the future. Treat's on me :). And keep those memes coming.

text:

text:

text:
Priank bhaiii!!
Mai abhi hi completely bhool chuka hu maine kya likhke bottle me gaada tha. Aaj se dus saal baad to koi clue hi nhi hoga ki kis baare me likha tha. Tjhe to mai hmesha us incident se yaad krunga jab ek motii ldki tere peeche pd gyi thi Antaragini me XD. 20 April k baad saare nightouts bde surreal se the. Ek to tmhari paagal wing k saath  wo sunrise yaad rhega mereko. Aur bhai A6 me lights aur tables lgake  bohot ambience bnaskte the tmlog koi na. Bangalore me milte hai jald hi.

text:
Mittal bhaii!!
I have utmost respect and admiration for you. Kaafi chaap k rkha tha har jagah.
Apne wing k alag hi masaala the tum. Bitching krne ka asli mazaa to bhai tmhaare saath hi hai. Hmesha yaad rkhna sbse pehla face cleanup mai krwaaya tha tmhara aur skin care bhi start krwaaya tha mai. End me tere saath cap mask shades lgake IITK ka Naples bnak rkh diya tha. Aur bhai tu tension na le tu bas bangalore aa alag mazze krwwaunga udhar.

text:
Aur bhaii!! IITK ka sbse chill bnda lgta hai tu. Second year summers me jab kuch project/course me dimaag kharaab krne jaarha hota tha to tjhe dekhta tha mast cooler k saamne first bowl se last bowl tak match dekhta tha. Sahi me yeh lgta tha ki mai bhi pause button dabake chill maarskta hu kuch aafat nhi aajayegi.Aise hi rehna life k small moments appreciate krte rehna.  All the best for your future bhai!!
Bajpaii!!
author: Somesh  Bajpai

text:
Yo Goel!!
EE200 ki quizzes se leke P2P ki quizzes tak tu to ha same rha pr maine pdhna chor diya(teri wajah se).  Second year to third-year ka transition bohot drastic sa hai CCD chore k 330 k baad MT jaana would remain one of my fondest memories. Aur UGP mere akele k bas ki baat to thi nhi so I owe you a lot in career terms too XD kyuki uske  bina to intern bhi nhi lgni thi.  UGP ki presentation k pehle daaru pilaaya tu yeh khud se to mai kbhi nhi krta XD. As Lab partners apne goals bde aligned the jitni jaldi ho ske nikalna hai. Aur zyaada chill guy waala persona na dikhaaya kar mjhe presi election me Saurav dubey k saaamne aur Day 1 ki raat me teri phat te dekhi hai maine. And mini quizzes me strategise krna tere left me ye hai mere right me isko baithalete hai was so fun when I think about it now. 
YN singh k text ki Tshirt bnwaate hai :P.Thanks for making batti bearable for me. Love you man (and this feels so gay that I won't ever say that again atleast sober to nhi)
Bajpai
author: Somesh  Bajpai
